snippet.title: Diana Roma and Oliver play Different Jobs and Professions
snippet.description:
Explore different professions with Diana, Roma and baby Oliver. With this compilation, the little ones will discover what a doctor does, or a policeman, auto mechanic, musician, fireman, baker, artist, hairdresser, astronaut, builders and and more! Introducing about Job and Occupation names early is important for kids to increase their motivation to study. An excellent resource for early childhood education.
Thanks for watching!
